							<h1>Welcome to Bellis!</h1>
							
							<p><b>Bellis Fruit Bars are wholly South Australian owned and managed, proudly manufacturing quality and value for money, dried fruit based confectionery.</b></p>
							
							
							
							<p>Bellis was first established in 1952 and since has become Australia's number one producer of school fruit bars and fruit based products.</p>
						
